    "uen": "202303329R",
    "description": "<p>Suntec Construction Engineering Pte. Ltd. originated from Jianxin Engineering Installation Co., Ltd. in Suzhou, China. As a professional mechanical and electrical installation contractor, we specialize in the production and installation of large-scale air conditioning, HVAC, fire protection, process, and various special gas pipelines in clean rooms. Our services also cover multiple fields, including construction, manufacturing, energy, and transportation.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;We have a highly qualified and experienced professional team. Our technical personnel have many years of experience in mechanical and electrical engineering and can provide customers with comprehensive and high-quality technical support and services.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;We have always been committed to providing customers with the best quality services, adhering to the service concept of \"customer first, quality first\", strictly following national standards and customer requirements, and ensuring that each project can be completed on time, with quality, and quantity.</p>\n<p>In the future, we will continue to adhere to the development concept of \"people-oriented, technological innovation\", continuously improve our service level and quality, continuously explore and innovate, and provide customers with more high-quality, efficient, and comprehensive mechanical and electrical equipment installation and technical services.</p>",
